html(lang="en")
    head
        meta(charset="UTF-8")
        meta(http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge")
        meta(name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0")

        link(rel="stylesheet" href="styles/styles.css")
        title Alvin Cousins | About
        link(rel="apple-touch-icon" sizes="180x180" href="/apple-touch-icon.png")
        link(rel="icon" type="image/png" sizes="32x32" href="/favicon-32x32.png")
        link(rel="icon" type="image/png" sizes="16x16" href="/favicon-16x16.png")
        link(rel="manifest" href="/site.webmanifest")
    body
        div(class="content")
            div(class="content__main")
                h1(class="side-heading") ABOUT
                div(class="content__flex-wrapper")
                    //- div(class="content__left")
                    div(class="paragraphs") 
                        p(class="paragraphs__string") Hi, Iâ€™m Alvin Cousins, an aspiring web developer, based in London, UK.
                        p(class="paragraphs__string") I have been working towards a new career path in tech since December 2020. This comes after 10 years in the construction industry as an Architectural Lighting Designer & Consultant and as an Architectural Assistant before that. These years in construction have given me:
                            ul
                                li A strong foundation in problem solving and design beyond mere aesthetics.
                                li Insight into how technologies and systems can elegantly interact and work seamlessly.
                                li Project delivery and management experience working in various teams with other designers and professionals from other disciplines. 
                        br
                        p(class="paragraphs__string") I always have a large appetite for learning new things and broadening my skills set whenever the opportunity arises. This attitude along with a humble mindset and willingness to adapt has served me well so far. I believe this puts me in good stead to successfully transition into an exciting new career in tech. 
                        br
                        a(class="paragraphs__cta" href="/contact") 
                            h3(class="break-medium white-hover") Contact Me
                    div(class="content__right")
                        img(class="content__right__img shadow" src="images/ac-mug-shot.jpg")

                    div(class="skills")
                        div(class="skills__section-title bold") Languages:
                        div(class="skills__inner")
                            each tech in technologies.data
                                if tech.category === "language"
                                    div(class="tech-icons__wrapper skills__icons")
                                        img(class="tech-icons__icon"  src=`../images/icons/technologies/${tech.skill}.svg` alt=tech.skill)
                                        span(class="tech-icons__text") #{tech.skill.replace("-", " ")}  
                        div(class="skills__section-title bold") Databases:
                        div(class="skills__inner")
                            each tech in technologies.data
                                if tech.category === "database"
                                    div(class="tech-icons__wrapper skills__icons")
                                        img(class="tech-icons__icon"  src=`../images/icons/technologies/${tech.skill}.svg` alt=tech.skill)
                                        span(class="tech-icons__text") #{tech.skill.replace("-", " ")}  
                        div(class="skills__section-title bold") Frameworks, Libraries and Services:
                        div(class="skills__inner")
                            each tech in technologies.data
                                if tech.category === "other-tech"
                                    div(class="tech-icons__wrapper skills__icons")
                                        img(class="tech-icons__icon"  src=`../images/icons/technologies/${tech.skill}.svg` alt=tech.skill)
                                        span(class="tech-icons__text") #{tech.skill.replace("-", " ")}  
                        div(class="skills__section-title bold") Design Software:
                        div(class="skills__inner")
                            each tech in technologies.data
                                if tech.category === "design"
                                    div(class="tech-icons__wrapper skills__icons")
                                        img(class="tech-icons__icon"  src=`../images/icons/technologies/${tech.skill}.svg` alt=tech.skill)
                                        span(class="tech-icons__text") #{tech.skill.replace("-", " ")}  

                        
                    div
                        div(class="paragraph-text break bold") Relevant courses I have taken:
                        each course in courses.data
                            a(href=course.link)
                                span(class="paragraph-text bold") #{course.title} 
                            div(class="paragraph-text break") #{course.subHeading} 
                            if course.otherLinks
                                div(class="paragraph-text small break") #{course.description}
                                each link in course.otherLinks
                                    a(href=link.link)
                                        div(class="paragraph-text small break-big") - #{link.description}
                            else 
                                div(class="paragraph-text small break-big") #{course.description}
                            
                    

            include sun-nav.pug
  
